=head1 DESCRIPTION

The filter applied to C<ListProfileObjects> response to include profile
objects with the specified index values.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> KeyName => Str

A searchable identifier of a profile object. The predefined keys you
can use to search for C<_asset> include: C<_assetId>, C<_assetName>,
and C<_serialNumber>. The predefined keys you can use to search for
C<_case> include: C<_caseId>. The predefined keys you can use to search
for C<_order> include: C<_orderId>.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Values => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

A list of key values.



